Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.84,0:22:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你會怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.17,0:22:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,A，暗暗守護
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.59,0:22:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,B，積極地與她交流
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.35,0:22:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,C，就是反對
